Shell Canada Ltd, 72 pct ownedby Royal Dutch/Shell Group &lt;RD> &lt;ST>, scheduled its annualmaintenance refinery shutdowns during the next two months,company spokeswoman Judy Wish said.    Wish said refineries will stockpile production before theshutdowns to maintain normal supply while maintenance iscarried out.    Production at Shell's major refinery at Strathcona Alberta,will be closed for about one month, Wish said.    There will be no layoffs associated with the refinerymaintenance, she added. Reuter&#3;